{"tid":17718,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"高登仔長命百歲 想活到150歲 這輩子就不要做愛","createTime":"2016-12-02T02:46:09.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-02T05:43:23.000Z","uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f03fc6c01bdce31df271f4302af818178f7bf5d8","tid":17718,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T02:46:09.000Z","msg":"英國一名36歲科學家札佛隆科夫(Alex Zhavoronkov)近日表示，如果人類想要長命百歲，活到150歲，「這輩子最好都不要做愛」。<br />\n<br />\n據英國《鏡報》報導，札佛隆科夫說，做愛、婚姻、養兒、享受物質都是阻礙長壽的因素，讓人分心，如果能摒除這些因子，人類就能活得長長久久。他在新書《不老的一代》(Ageless Generation)中指出，沒有性愛的生活，人類可以活得「很遠，很長久」。至於札佛隆科夫有沒有性生活？他說：「我偶爾做愛，但不是永久的基礎，我都跟其他科學家做。」他也指出，做愛後的互動其實很無聊。<br />\n<br />\n想要「長生不老」，札佛隆科夫除了提倡禁慾，他也認為規律運動和飲食節制是非常重要的，他自稱一天消耗1600~1700卡路里的熱量，並多吃水果、優格和蛋白棒。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n41j聲演：<a href=\"http://m.appledailytw.com/column/article/9/rnews/20151010/708587\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.appledailytw.com%2Fcolumn%2Farticle%2F9%2Frnews%2F20151010%2F708587&d=9YhXM5wGpBmAIWfwXK7ScBpDoU409oZNeObLMRtCPuc%3D&h=6f2b04ac\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.appledailytw.com/column/article/9/rnews/20151010/708587</a>"},{"pid":"3f4035603eb34ac483515aa6e8031599113d12fb","tid":17718,"uid":6232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T02:47:29.000Z","msg":"個個高登仔都有150歲命<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dce5bb2509678d0e27909c12546d582cb8481670","tid":17718,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T02:47:45.000Z","msg":"唔做愛活到1500歲都冇用啦"},{"pid":"f235fc79ff2eb46b81f858483ba0ce3f11372acb","tid":17718,"uid":17542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T02:47:56.000Z","msg":"他說：「我偶爾做愛，但不是永久的基礎，我都跟其他科學家做。」<br />\n<br />\ngay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dd9605d37798643dd2055e4c7ad697e3ad182d0","tid":17718,"u